Lesson 1.1 - Welcome to your health journey

---------- [L1]

RSS feed link: https://rss.com/podcasts/footnerdprogram/362109/

Video link: https://youtu.be/8UYn2qAFwmc

Creators: Ruth & Nick

Framework:

- Thank you for being here
- Our core values
- Critical thinking
- Proof of work
- Experiments
- Accountability (partner & pod)
- Creating purpose
- Content layers & program structure
- Planning out your journey through behaviour design

STUDENT PACK LINK: https://tfchardgoods.com/products/fnp-student-pack-2021

[use code: "22nerdpack" for nerd pricing which gives you $225 off the retail price]

Audio lesson notes:
- detailed notes and timestamps from the audio lesson [to be added in future]


Experiments (nano to macro)

- Start a log (digital or paper)
- Intention statement: when will I do my daily log each day?
- Design accountability prompts (notebook location, phone alert, telling family members)
- Introduce yourseld to your partner, do a zoom call to meet them, learn three interesting things about them
- Crafting your daily hour (when, where, making up lost days)

